text: Bogorodsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Sukkulovsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 78 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Yermekeyevo, 4 km from Sukkulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Bogorodsky, Republic of Bashkortostan
